+Three entry points:
+  - Web UI (Next.js) â€” primary experience (REST API + SSE streaming)
+  - MCP Server â€” AI clients (Claude Desktop, Cursor) query KB directly
+  - n8n + Slack â€” team members query from Slack via webhook workflow
